{"tid":289948,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"活得比你好？梁特豪言願與港青交換生命","createTime":"2017-06-19T11:49:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T12:47:56.000Z","uid":42536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aeb847fa3bf0baf142a02cf5b26b08041f745ed0","tid":289948,"uid":42536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T11:49:45.000Z","msg":"任期尚餘不足兩周的特首梁振英，近日在多個中共喉舌亮相，其中《人民日報》及其海外版專訪梁特的版本，有一句可圈可點的言論，竟未見有其他官媒提及。文末指，梁振英聲言很羡慕今時今日的港青，因他們的起點「比我們那個時代好」，稱「願意與香港任何一位年輕人」交換生命。翻查資料，梁特早於前年底和本月初，均曾發表類似言論，豪言「如果我今天係一個香港隨便一間中學嘅中學生，我可以有更大嘅發揮」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170619/56847231\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170619%2F56847231&d=vpd5XgWtkLViUnhvB70SY9ZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=a2063f87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170619%2F56847231&h=fa887a16\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170619/56847231</a>"},{"pid":"274c09dea16fc4e03e2e3b3198787299affc55f3","tid":289948,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T12:42:31.000Z","msg":"落地府搵啦"},{"pid":"07e541bd5ff305a4ebdbee124b2e67fb26375a06","tid":289948,"uid":604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T12:45:06.000Z","msg":"用個剩返一日命嘅港青同你換"},{"pid":"33ca4b8b2e37265eb7e15c18ac0a000f585b84a3","tid":289948,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T12:47:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/15UqaAUbOLU/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F15UqaAUbOLU%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&d=vpd5XgWtkLViUnhvB70SY9ZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=5edefdeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://i.ytimg.com/vi/15UqaAUbOLU/maxresdefault.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"5ca6ac37ab5589c66055f6010a73c19419c9a0f2","tid":289948,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci